{"tid":280254,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「多圖食評」羅湖商業城彩碟軒早茶","createTime":"2017-06-12T03:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T03:43:55.000Z","uid":9769,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f58a0548127ae3c9e1d64f31fd5cba8302f571db","tid":280254,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:08:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/105102_5131a8e1da29ee5aed9dcb0cfd320270.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F105102_5131a8e1da29ee5aed9dcb0cfd320270.jpg&h=2f8250fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/110755_6149a42638dfc87a21d5a444dae031b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F110755_6149a42638dfc87a21d5a444dae031b1.jpg&h=eb483e45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/105104_b716db6b7024d0766dba66b46e5f5e60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F105104_b716db6b7024d0766dba66b46e5f5e60.jpg&h=949c6897&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/105231_008a8296b2ac369848da0cfcdf8de6e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F105231_008a8296b2ac369848da0cfcdf8de6e0.jpg&h=89c3040d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本去香格里拉間「香宮」食，但佢要11點先開門，餓到仆街，黎彩碟軒食住先。<br />\n<br />\n成日一入去就放低包紙巾想屈多幾蚊，叫佢收走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蝦餃個芯仲未熱透，似係一早整定係雪櫃拿出來蒸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n排骨好滑，用筷子好難夾，我唔食芋頭的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叉燒腸ok, 隻碟又重又熱，想搬搬個位置小心熱親，豉油是分開一碟上的。"},{"pid":"e884b75849fb3a087ce55e53e5c05c4ba151775a","tid":280254,"uid":117689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:13:44.000Z","msg":"而家中國食野咁貴"},{"pid":"ecfdbe41443dd00b4ce7fb186b6a6e0790567483","tid":280254,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:14:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家中國食野咁貴</blockquote><br />\n係呀⋯⋯"},{"pid":"2f939df143200decffe4d303e319eaef4d9203df","tid":280254,"uid":19728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"次次都係食哂先影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61695af8a15c6097a0df47a1b145297b233e5d0","tid":280254,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:15:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次都係食哂先影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50c91af15fb6f11cc28e9d6f5ea187fad234df6","tid":280254,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:42:38.000Z","msg":"影隻碟有咩睇"},{"pid":"2629eb406a7910584d181613900cb07972c707cd","tid":280254,"uid":92278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:43:55.000Z","msg":"走啦 大6仔"}]}